commit.message: Painting is now activated white the screen is pressed, rather than a tap to turn on/off. This way seems more intuitive on the user end
fixed unstable paint toggle. Is now a tap gesture rather than a long touch gesture
Added synchronized painting between users, the end goal of this project
Added plane stability to both host and client ends. higher accuracy made at the sacrifice of longer user setup. May change
Updated Labels to match various statuses
Removed leftover data (third-party) used in learning process
2 way live tracking. Possible MVP. Could add painting, but happy ARt is done
Live tracking in place. not the best, but in place!
